<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL24">
<l>veḷḷanīr parantu pāyum viripoḻi laraṅkan taṉṉuṭ</l>
<l>kaḷḷaṉār kiṭanta vāṟuṅ kamalanaṉ mukamuṅ kaṇṭu</l>
<l>muḷḷamē valiyai pōlu moruvaṉeṉ ṟuṇara māṭṭāy</l>
<l>kaḷḷamē kātal ceytuṉ kaḷḷattē kaḻikkiṉ ṟāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart! Even after seeing [His] beautiful lotus face</l>
<l rend="indent">and the way the Deceitful [Lord] reclined</l>
<l rend="indent">inside Raṅgam with extensive groves where flood water spreads and flows,</l>
<l rend="indent">it seems you are hardened.</l>
<l rend="indent">You will not realise that [He] is unique.</l>
<l>Bearing [Him] false love, you are wasting time in your falsehood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
